category.title: Public Property Bench
category.description: Outdoor benches are wholly owned by the government though paid for or sponsored by private intrerests whether profit or non-profit.

category.title: Public Private Property Bench
category.description: Outdoor benches that are wholly owned by private intrerests and reside on private property for the benefit of both the public and the firm.

category.title: Private Property Bench
category.description: Outdoor benches is wholly owned by private interests and reside on private property of the benefit of the firm patrons and workers.
